entries.title: Endor System: Satellite Delivery
entries.title_d: Remain in the Endor system, pickup, and deliver satellites to the engineers. Even though several other shuttles managed to get away, command cannot worry about those right now. The detection satellites that ring the system were taken offline, which is how the Bothans managed to avoid detection and capture the vessels. Those satellites need to be replaced immediately. Pickup two satellites and deliver them to the engineers who will put them back into place.
